        "\n",
        "<br>\n",
        "\n",
        "-   Flucloxacillin (also dicloxacillin?) activates the pregnane X receptor (PXR), which can induce the expression of CYP450 and UGT enzymes, and P-gP transporters\n",
        "\n",
